DESCRIPTION:Hi All\,\n\nThis Assignment is to publish a Webpage with GitHub
  Pages. You’ll build a simple\, well-structured personal webpage and hos
 t it for free using GitHub Pages. By the end\, your site will be publicly 
 accessible at a URL like https://<your-username>.github.io/ (user site) 
 or https://<your-username>.github.io/<repo-name>/ (project site).\n\nNote
 : We do not require any specific content in your webpage. You are free 
 to choose the topic\, purpose\, and style (resume/CV\, portfolio\, “Abou
 t me\,” a hobby\, course notes\, or anything else appropriate (e.g.\, pi
 cs\, videos\, audio files)). The focus of this assignment is learning the 
 process of creating/publishing and hosting\, not what the site is about.\n
 \nThanks & Regards\,\n\nZhengkun\n\n \n\nReferences to Follow (Must Read)
 :\n\n[https://docs.github.com/en/pages/getting-started-with-github-pages/c
 reating-a-github-pages-siteLinks to an external site.] (https://docs.githu
 b.com/en/pages/getting-started-with-github-pages/creating-a-github-pages-s
 ite)\n\n[https://www.khanacademy.org/computing/computer-programming/html-c
 ss/web-development-tools/a/hosting-your-website-on-githubLinks to an exter
 nal site.] (https://www.khanacademy.org/computing/computer-programming/htm
 l-css/web-development-tools/a/hosting-your-website-on-github)\n\nWebsite T
 emplates:\n\n[https://github.com/website-templatesLinks to an external sit
 e.] (https://github.com/website-templates)\n\nVideo:\n\n[https://www.youtu
 be.com/watch?v=e5AwNU3Y2esLinks to an external site.] (https://www.youtube
 .com/watch?v=e5AwNU3Y2es)\n\n(Please also do search(es) on YouTube for the
  tutorials you'd like to watch)
